<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= pageTitle %> | DAMORE</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css" />
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: #f6f4ef;
      color: #111;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .page {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 48px 20px 80px;
    }

    .community-head {
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .community-head h1 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 34px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .community-head p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #777;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .community-tabs {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    .community-tabs a {
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd2c4;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #fff;
      color: #444;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .community-tabs a.active {
      background: #111;
      color: #fff;
      border-color: #111;
    }

    .empty-box {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e8e0d4;
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 70px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/header') %>

  <div class="page">
    <div class="community-head">
      <h1>리뷰</h1>
      <p>고객 리뷰를 모아보는 공간입니다.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="community-tabs">
      <a href="/community/notice">공지사항</a>
      <a href="/community/review" class="active">리뷰</a>
      <a href="/community/event">이벤트</a>
      <a href="/community/customer">고객센터</a>
    </div>

    <div class="empty-box">
      리뷰 페이지 준비중입니다.<br />
      추후 상품 후기 리스트와 상세 보기 기능이 들어갈 예정입니다.
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>